<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA524_11_IH_0001_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    <script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema524_11.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema524_11_ih_0001" data-current-page="page_1, page_2, page_3, page_4, page_5, page_6">
      <section class="title puzzle type2">
        <div class="puzzle_tit">
          <span class="tag" lang="y">창의</span>
          <span class="tit" lang="y">
            <span class="emph">퍼즐</span>
            <span class="txt1">로</span>
            <span class="txt2">정리해요</span>
          </span>
        </div>
        <h2 lang="y">독도에는 독도를 지키는 독도경비대가 있습니다. 소수의 곱셈을 하여 곱이 적힌 땅에 쓰여 있는 글자를 쓰고, 독도경비대의 주소를 알아보세요.</h2>
      </section>
      <section class="contents">
        <div class="flex justify_center gap_40">
          <div class="img"><img src="../../common_practice/img/EMA524_11_IH/0001_img.svg" alt="" width="550" /></div>
          <div class="question_box">
            <div class="list_quiz">
              <div class="item">
                <span class="num">1</span>
                7×2.3
              </div>
              <div class="item">
                <span class="num">2</span>
                0.16×6
              </div>
              <div class="item">
                <span class="num">3</span>
                2.4×3
              </div>
              <div class="item">
                <span class="num">4</span>
                0.4×0.8
              </div>
              <div class="item">
                <span class="num">5</span>
                5.4×1.3
              </div>
              <div class="item">
                <span class="num">6</span>
                1.27×4.2
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="input_area">
              <span class="txt" lang="y">경상남도 울릉군 울릉읍</span>
              <div class="bottom flex align_center gap_4 mt_40">
                <div class="input_wrap">
                  <span class="num">①</span>
                  <math-field data-answer-single="독"></math-field>
                </div>
                <div class="input_wrap">
                  <span class="num">②</span>
                  <math-field data-answer-single="도"></math-field>
                </div>
                <div class="input_wrap">
                  <span class="num">③</span>
                  <math-field data-answer-single="이"></math-field>
                </div>
                <div class="input_wrap">
                  <span class="num">④</span>
                  <math-field data-answer-single="사"></math-field>
                </div>
                <div class="input_wrap">
                  <span class="num">⑤</span>
                  <math-field data-answer-single="부"></math-field>
                </div>
                <div class="input_wrap">
                  <span class="num">⑥</span>
                  <math-field data-answer-single="길"></math-field>
                </div>
                &nbsp;
                <span>55</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
